          Web3Templates
        </a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </Container>
</footer>
<style lang="scss">
  [astro-icon] {
    @apply h-full w-8 cursor-pointer;
    &:hover,
    &:focus,
    &:active {
      @apply text-primary;
    }
  }
</style>
